**Bitcoin by MtGox Mobile** (formerly branded as **MtGox Live**) was a mobile app that brought many of the features of the [[Mt._Gox]] exchange's website to the mobile platform. The app was used to buy and sell bitcoins, view the orderbook, and see trading history.

##History
This service was first seen in early May, 2011, but first appeared in the forum on May 29, 2011. (2.1) It first appeared under the domain **mtgoxlive.bco.in** but switched to **mtgoxlive.com**. (2.1)

On July 19, 2011 the service was acquired by Mt. Gox. (2.2)

